org.apache.poi.ddf

Interface EscherRecordFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultEscherRecordFactory, HSLFEscherRecordFactory 

    public interface EscherRecordFactory
    The escher record factory interface allows for the creation of escher records from a pointer into a data array.(escher记录工厂接口允许从指针创建到数据数组的escher记录。)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      EscherRecord createRecord(byte[] data, int offset)
      Generates an escher record including any children contained under that record.(生成escher记录，包括该记录下包含的任何子项。)

    • Method Detail

      • createRecord

        EscherRecord createRecord(byte[] data,
                          int offset)
        Generates an escher record including any children contained under that record. An exception is thrown if the record could not be generated.(生成escher记录，包括该记录下包含的任何子项。如果无法生成记录，则会引发异常。)
        Parameters:
        data - The byte array containing the records(data -包含记录的字节数组)
        offset - The starting offset into the byte array(Offset -字节数组的开始偏差)
        Returns:
        The generated escher record(生成的escher记录)
